PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION (a) to DISPOSE of eight parcels of land in favour of the CITY OF HULL, (b) LEASE to the CITY OF HULL two parcels of land, (c) GRANT an easement for a storm water facility to the CITY OF HULL, and (d) ACQUIRE from the CANADA LANDS COMPANY some 6.69 hectares of lands situated in Hull.
